graph TD
    %% Roles
    Start((Mulai)) --> Login[Halaman Login]
    Login --> Auth{Autentikasi}
    Auth -- Gagal --> Login
    Auth -- Berhasil --> RoleCheck{Cek Role?}

    %% Admin Flow
    RoleCheck -- ADMIN --> AdminDash[Admin Dashboard]
    AdminDash --> ManageData[Kelola Data Master<br/>Kelas, Semester, MK, Kategori]
    AdminDash --> ManageStudents[Kelola Akun Mahasiswa]
    AdminDash --> ManageAssign[Kelola Tugas]
    
    ManageAssign --> CreateAssign[Buat/Edit Tugas]
    CreateAssign --> AddQuestions[Input Soal & Opsi Jawaban]
    AddQuestions --> Publish{Publish?}
    Publish -- Ya --> Published[Tugas Tersedia untuk Mahasiswa]
    
    AdminDash --> ViewReports[Lihat Laporan & Submisi]

    %% Student Flow
    RoleCheck -- STUDENT --> StudentDash[Student Dashboard]
    StudentDash --> ViewAssign[Lihat Daftar Tugas Tersedia]
    ViewAssign --> WorkAssign[Workspace Pengerjaan Tugas]
    WorkAssign --> Submit[Submit Jawaban]
    Submit --> CalcScore[Kalkulasi Nilai Otomatis]
    CalcScore --> Finish((Selesai))
